    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Sports Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Manny Being Manny Is Hurting the Red Sox,'' March 18: I watched Manny Ramírez play in person when he was with the Cleveland Indians from 1994 to 2000 and held my breath when balls were hit to left field.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Sports Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Manny Being Manny Is Hurting the Red Sox,'' March 18: I watched Manny Ramírez play in person when he was with the Cleveland Indians from 1994 to 2000 and held my breath when balls were hit to left field.</p>
        <p>He is playing a much better left field in Boston than he ever did in Cleveland. In fact, we often shake our heads and say, ''Boy, those folks in Boston really taught him to play the outfield.''</p>
        <p>Deborah A. Smith  Cleveland Heights, Ohio</p>
      </block>
